----------------------------------------------------------------------
CHANGELOG                                         Collaborilla project
----------------------------------------------------------------------

----- Bug and Feature Tracking ---------------------------------------

The Collaborilla bugtracker can be accessed at

  http://kmr.nada.kth.se/mantis/

----- Collaborilla 1.0 ---------------------------------------------

First stable version of Collaborilla. Released together with Conzilla 2.1.

- 0000077: [Basic Design] Rework client interface: e.g. set() and clear() methods for dealing with Sets (hannes)
- 0000076: [Basic Design] Remove methods and server commands for "modify" (hannes)
- 0000075: [Basic Design] Naming of the URI fields should be changed (hannes)
- 0000073: [Basic Design] Collections in CollaborillaAccessible should be Sets (hannes)
- 0000066: [Bug] setContainerRevision() sends the wrong command (hannes)
- 0000065: [Basic Design] getDataSet() should be part of the CollaborillaAccessible interface (hannes)
- 0000064: [Basic Design] Serializable data container to enable (not only) caching on client side (hannes)
- 0000063: [Basic Design] Implement a buffered client to make caching for read-access possible (hannes)
- 0000060: [Bug] Different identifiers collide in certain situations (hannes)
- 0000059: [Basic Design] Protect "old" revisions from being modified (hannes)
- 0000054: [Basic Design] Subversion revisions not assigned to information node revisions (hannes)

----- Collaborilla 0.9 ---------------------------------------------

Based on the thesis prototype. (Subversion tag "20060521-thesis")
